textBeforeTable: The Eclipse SDK includes the Eclipse Platform, Java development tools, and Plug-in Development Environment, including source and both user and programmer documentation. If you aren't sure which download you want... then you probably want this one. Eclipse does not include a Java runtime environment (JRE). You will need a 1.4.2 level or higher Java runtime or Java development kit (JDK) installed on your machine in order to run Eclipse. Click here if you need help finding a Java runtime.
